   <text>
      <body>
         <pb facs="1872_06_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>
            <seg rend="left">
               <hi rend="latintype">via <placeName ref="K00515">Marseille</placeName>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <seg rend="right">
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00522">Hamburg</placeName>, <date when="1872-06-06">6. Juni
                            1872</date>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <lb/> Herren <hi rend="latintype">
               <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. Kniffler &amp; Co</orgName>
            </hi>
            <lb/>
            <seg rend="center">
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <hi rend="underline">
                     <placeName ref="K00525">Yokohama</placeName>. <placeName ref="K00502">Japan</placeName>
                  </hi>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <lb/> Ich bestätige <choice>
               <abbr>m/</abbr>
               <expan> mein</expan>
            </choice> ergebenes vom <date when="1872-05-28">28. <choice>
                  <abbr>v. M</abbr>
                  <expan> vorigen Monats</expan>
               </choice>
            </date> und<lb/> überreiche Ihnen einliegend <term type="commercial" ref="K01574">Factura</term> über Ihnen<lb/> ⅌ <hi rend="latintype">Steamer via <placeName ref="K00523">London</placeName>
            </hi> für meine Rechnung zu ge-<lb/> führte 100 <hi rend="latintype">Stg <hi rend="superscript">54</hi>/56 j <unclear>Imp</unclear> Cloth</hi> deren
                bestemög-<lb/> lichen Verkauf Sie <choice>
               <abbr>gef.</abbr>
               <expan> gefällig</expan>
            </choice> besorgen wollen.<lb/> Für den Betrag von<lb/>
            <seg rend="center">
               <hi rend="underline">
                  <term type="currency" ref="K01830">B<hi rend="superscript">co</hi>
                  </term>₻ <measure type="currency" unit="mbanco" quantity="11699.9">11699.8.</measure>
               </hi>
               <figure>
                  <figDesc>Zeichen für L. Kniffler Co. Zweiteiliges Symbol für Firma Kniffler oben Lettern mit starken Serifen L. K. &amp; C darunter mit einem Strich getrennt und Ebenfalls mit starken Serifen C</figDesc>
               </figure> 150/9. </seg>
            <lb/> belieben Sie mich auf <hi rend="latintype">
               <term type="logistic" ref="K01584">Consignations</term> Conto</hi>
            <choice>
               <abbr>gef</abbr>
               <expan> gefällig</expan>
            </choice> zu<lb/> erkennen_<lb/> Soweit geschrieben, erreicht mich Ihr<lb/> Werthes
                vom <date when="1872-04-23">23. April</date>
            <hi rend="latintype">via <placeName ref="K00556">Amerika</placeName>
            </hi> mit<lb/>
            <seg rend="center">
               <term type="commercial" ref="K01522">₤</term>
               <hi rend="underline">
                  <measure type="currency" unit="britPound" quantity="103.25">103. 2.
                            5</measure>
               </hi>
               <hi rend="superscript">a</hi>/ <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00523">London</placeName>
               </hi> die ich, wenn</seg>
            <lb/> in Ordnung gehend, zur Ebnung des ausge-<lb/> gebenen Nettobetrages verwenden
                werde.<lb/> Wenn Ihnen Buchungen, etc. bisher<lb/> unvollkommen erschien, so hat es
                seinen Grund<lb/> darin, daß sowohl Pöste von fester Rechnung<lb/> als <hi rend="latintype">
               <term type="commercial" ref="K01535">à metà</term>
            </hi> auf derselben <hi rend="latintype">Conto</hi> gebucht wurden, ich werde<lb/>
            <lb/>
            <seg rend="right">
               <hi rend="latintype">verte!</hi>
            </seg>
            <lb/>
            <seg rend="left">1 Einlagen<lb/>1 <term type="commercial" ref="K01574">
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Fact.</abbr>
                     <expan>Factura</expan>
                  </choice>
               </term>
               <lb/>2 Noten</seg>
         </p>
         <pb facs="1872_06_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p> für die Folge alle Briefe <choice>
               <abbr>u </abbr>
               <expan> und</expan>
            </choice> Documente für Ihre<lb/>
            <choice>
               <abbr>w.</abbr>
               <expan> werten</expan>
            </choice> anderen Firmen stets durch Ihre Hände gehen<lb/> lassen.<lb/> Unter der
                Falte behändige ich Ihnen noch<lb/> Frachtnoten über<lb/>
            <add style="writingMode: vertical-lr; textOrientation: sideways-left" resp="other" place="marginLeft">
               <hi rend="underline">
                  <term type="commercial" ref="K01536">M 441</term>
               </hi>
            </add>
            <table>
               <row>
                  <cell>
                     <figure>
                        <figDesc>Zeichen für L. Kniffler Co. Zweiteiliges Symbol für Firma Kniffler oben Lettern mit starken Serifen L. K. &amp; C darunter mit einem Strich getrennt und Ebenfalls mit starken Serifen B</figDesc>
                     </figure>
                  </cell>
                  <cell>306-315. betragend</cell>
                  <cell>
                     <term type="currency" ref="K01830">B<hi rend="superscript">co</hi>
                     </term> ₻ <measure type="currency" unit="mbanco" quantity="81.11">81.
                                11.</measure> ⅌ <date when="1872-05-28">28. <hi rend="latintype">Mai</hi>
                     </date>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>- <choice>
                        <abbr>＂</abbr>
                        <expan>L K &amp; C B</expan>
                     </choice> - </cell>
                  <cell>306-312. <choice>
                        <abbr>＂</abbr>
                        <expan>betragend</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </cell>
                  <cell>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>＂</abbr>
                        <expan>Bco</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <measure type="currency" unit="mbanco" quantity="274.8">274. 8</measure>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>＂</abbr>
                        <expan>⅌</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <date when="1872-05-29">29 <hi rend="latintype">Mai</hi>
                     </date>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell>u. Spesen <hi rend="superscript">a</hi>/ 1 Musterpacket 306/315</cell>
                  <cell>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>＂</abbr>
                        <expan>Bco</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <measure type="currency" unit="mbanco" quantity="7.7">7. 7.</measure>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>＂</abbr>
                        <expan>⅌</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <date when="1872-06-03">3 <hi rend="latintype">Juni</hi>
                     </date>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <lb/> welche Beträge Sie mir <choice>
               <abbr>gef.</abbr>
               <expan> gefällig</expan>
            </choice> zuschreiben wollen.__<lb/> Ich beziehe mich noch auf die Einlage für<lb/>
                Ihr <choice>
               <abbr>w/</abbr>
               <expan> wertes</expan>
            </choice> Haus in <hi rend="latintype">
               <placeName ref="K00545">Hiogo</placeName>
            </hi> und grüße Sie<lb/>
            <seg rend="right">Freundschaftlichst:<lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <hi rend="underline">
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01064">H. C. Bock</orgName>
                  </hi>
               </hi>
            </seg>
         </p>
         <pb facs="1872_06_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1872_06_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_4.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <p>
            <seg rend="center">
               <stamp style="round" type="postal">
                  <placeName ref="K00525">YOKOHAMA</placeName>
                  <lb/>
                  <date when="1872-07-24">24<lb/>J<unclear>UIL.</unclear>
                     <lb/>72</date>
                  <lb/>B<hi rend="superscript">AU</hi> FRANCAIS</stamp>
               <lb/>
               <lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <hi rend="underline">via <placeName ref="K00515">Marseille</placeName>
                  </hi>
               </hi>
               <lb/>
               <stamp style="rectangular" type="postal">P. D</stamp>
               <stamp style="round" type="postal">ALLEMAGNE<lb/>2 <unclear reason="illegible">1|</unclear>7<lb/>
                  <unclear reason="illegible">UIL</unclear>
                  <lb/>
                  <unclear>72</unclear>
                  <gap agent="rubbed"/>
               </stamp>
               <stamp style="round" type="postal">
                  <placeName ref="K00525">HAMBURG</placeName>
                  <lb/>F.<lb/>
                  <date when="1872-06-05">5 6<lb/>72</date>
                  <lb/>N 8 -3.N. 1.</stamp>
               <lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">Messrs<lb/>
                  <orgName ref="K01004" type="firm">L. Kniffler &amp; C<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>
                  </orgName>
                  <lb/>
                  <hi rend="underline">
                     <placeName ref="K00525">Yokohama</placeName>
                  </hi>
                  <lb/>
                  <placeName ref="K00502">Japan</placeName>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <lb/>
            <add style="writingMode: vertical-lr; textOrientation: sideways-right" resp="other" place="marginRight">1872<lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00522">Hamburg</placeName>
                  <date when="1872-06-05">5 Juni</date>
                  <lb/>
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01064">H. C. Bock</orgName>
                  <lb/> R<hi rend="underline">
                     <date when="1872-06-24">24 July</date>
                  </hi>
                  <lb/>
                  <date when="1872-08-06">Aug 6</date>
               </hi>
            </add>
         </p>
      </body>
   </text>
   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1872_06_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>via Marseille Hamburg, 6th June 1872<lb/> Herren L. Kniffler &amp; Co<lb/>Yokohama.
                Japan<lb/>I confirm my respectful letter from 28th of last month <lb/>and supply you
                with the enclosed invoice for the <lb/>100 pieces 54/56 j Imp[?] cloth delivered to
                you <lb/>⅌ steamer via London for my account, the most <lb/>favourable sale of which
                you will kindly take care of. <lb/>For the amount of <lb/>Bco ₻ 11,699.8. <lb/>
            <figure>
               <figDesc>Sign for L. Kniffler Co. Two-part symbol for the Kniffler company, at the top letters L. K. &amp; C with strong serifs, below that, divided by a line, the letter C, also with strong serifs</figDesc>
            </figure> 150/9. <lb/>kindly credit me on the consignment account<lb/>please
                _<lb/>Just as I was writing this, your esteemed letter <lb/>from 23rd April via
                America reached me with<lb/>₤ 103. 2. 5 a/ London, which, if it is in order, <lb/>I
                will use for balancing the spent net amount.<lb/>If bookings etc. have so far seemed
                to you to<lb/>be incomplete, the reason for this lies in the fact <lb/>that some
                lots were also booked on fixed account <lb/>as à metà on the same account, I will
                from<lb/>p.t.o.<lb/>1 insert<lb/>1 invoice<lb/>2 notes</p>
         <pb facs="1872_06_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>now on have all letters and documents for <lb/>your other esteemed companies always
                pass through<lb/>your hands.<lb/>Enclosed I also supply you with the bills of lading
                for <lb/>⟨M 441⟩ <table>
               <row>
                  <cell>
                     <figure>
                        <figDesc>Sign for L. Kniffler Co. Two-part symbol for the Kniffler company, at the top letters L. K. &amp; C with strong serifs, below that, divided by a line, the letter B, also with strong serifs</figDesc>
                     </figure>
                  </cell>
                  <cell>306-315. amounting to</cell>
                  <cell>Bco ₻ 81. 11. ⅌ 28th May</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>- ＂ - </cell>
                  <cell>306-312. ＂ </cell>
                  <cell>＂ 274. 8 ＂ 29th May</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell>and expenses a/ 1 sample package 306/315</cell>
                  <cell>＂ 7. 7. ＂ 3rd June</cell>
               </row>
            </table> which amounts you will kindly credit me for.__<lb/>I finally refer you to
                the insert for your <lb/>esteemed house in Hiogo and send my greetings,<lb/>Yours
                most cordially<lb/>H. C. Bock</p>
         <pb facs="1872_06_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1872_06_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_4.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <p>YOKOHAMA<lb/>24<lb/>JUIL.[?]<lb/>72<lb/>BAU FRANCAIS<lb/>
            <lb/>via Marseille<lb/>P. DALLEMAGNE<lb/>2
                1|[?]7<lb/>UIL[?]<lb/>72[?][...]HAMBURG<lb/>F.<lb/>5 6<lb/>72<lb/>N 8 -3.N.
                1.<lb/>Messrs<lb/>L. Kniffler &amp; Co.<lb/>Yokohama<lb/>Japan<lb/>⟨1872<lb/>Hamburg
                5th June<lb/>H. C. Bock<lb/>R[eceived] 24th July<lb/>Aug 6th⟩</p>
      </body>
